title: Baker (Alice)
body: Ref.: A Summer in the Azores With a Glimpse of Madeira, Boston, 1882.

Azores: Group of islands in the North Atlantic.

Alice Baker: Author of the book 'A Summer in the Azores With a Glimpse of Madeira'.

1882: Year of publication of the book 'A Summer in the Azores With a Glimpse of Madeira'.
